snippet.title: The Guardian of Nature - Official Overview Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Meet Henry, a botanist, learn about the story, and see the gorgeous world of The Guardian of Nature in this trailer for the upcoming puzzle adventure game. The Guardian of Nature will be available on PC.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
